This update fixes bugs and improves the performance of the app.

NEW
• Behind the scenes, we did a lot of work to enable numbers from more countries - stay tuned for their roll-out!  (Currently, we offer numbers from: Australia, Austria, Belgium, Canada, Germany, Mauritius, Netherlands, United Kingdom, United States.)
• We added a message status indicator to the inbox

IMPROVEMENTS
• We drastically improved the creation of a phone number.
• [PREMIUM subscribers] Call forwarding now works with any phone number.

FIXED
• Multi Number users: placing a call from a contact now starts with choosing the number from which to call.

Our team works hard every day to improve your experience.
– Have feedback you want to tell us? Shoot us an email at: feedback@go-text.me
– If you have any issues, write us at: support@go-text.me
